Department of Justice,
that is discrimination.

42:31.015 --> 42:35.820 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
YASMEEN QURESHI: Education
policy professor
Suzanne Eckes is referring to a
letter the

42:35.920 --> 42:42.427 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
