"Dear Colleague" letter.

43:08.386 --> 43:13.057 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
YASMEEN QURESHI: However,
several Republican
state leaders are advising
schools to ignore

43:13.157 --> 43:16.627 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
