risk of losing
federal funding.

43:16.727 --> 43:21.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KENT OSTRANDER: Why does there
have to be
a new federal government law
telling everybody

43:21.866 --> 43:26.504 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
