43:28.773 --> 43:32.443 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Because states can make that
decision on their
own. Parents can make that
decision.

43:32.543 --> 43:37.782 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SUZANNE ECKES: I don't think
this is a Democrat
or Republican or liberal or
conservative issue.

43:37.882 --> 43:41.719 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This is a civil rights issue.
This isn't a
states' rights issue. This is a
civil rights

43:41.819 --> 43:47.225 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
issue. Transgender students, for
years, have
been ostracized in public
schools.

43:47.325 --> 43:52.730 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
YASMEEN QURESHI: Nearly half of
transgender
teens report having suicidal
thoughts. And

43:52.830 --> 43:57.201 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
