anxiety are
far higher than the average.

43:57.301 --> 44:00.638 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN: Good morning, Atherton High
School.

44:00.738 --> 44:06.110 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
YASMEEN QURESHI: It's been over
