44:19.757 --> 44:22.860 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
NATALIE STASTNY, Student,
Atherton High School:
It's just going to the bathroom.
You go do

44:22.960 --> 44:27.398 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
