44:30.601 --> 44:33.170 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NIJA MACKEY, Student, Atherton
High School:
Coming from, like, a religious
background,

44:33.271 --> 44:38.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
like, I am Christian, and people
don't necessarily
agree with that type of stuff.
But I have

44:38.843 --> 44:44.382 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
been going to this school for
two years, and
it's just routine. Like,
everyone gets to

44:44.482 --> 44:48.586 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the restroom, everyone gets out.
It's nothing,
nothing. It's not a big deal.

44:48.686 --> 44:52.490 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. THOMAS ABERLI: Something I
struggled with
originally was just
understanding the difference

44:52.590 --> 44:57.995 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
