issue. If

44:58.095 --> 45:02.767 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
any student said that they were
uncomfortable
with using a restroom, then they
can choose

45:02.867 --> 45:04.802 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
an alternate restroom.

45:04.902 --> 45:10.408 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we're not to compel other
people to act
differently just because they
make someone

45:10.508 --> 45:15.513 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
else feel uncomfortable. That is
not what
our country is about. That is
not a right

45:15.613 --> 45:21.719 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to privacy.
YASMEEN QURESHI: The school
provides access
